title: Crystal Palace 1-2 Swansea City: Zaragoza drags Eagles into relegation danger
text:
Crystal Palace 1-2 Swansea City: Zaragoza drags Eagles into relegation danger Getty 0 Jan 3, 2017 21:54:33 
A relegation six-pointer at Selhurst Park was settled by Angel Rangel's late winner, as Swansea City grabbed a vital 2-1 win over Crystal Palace to leave the Eagles hovering over the drop zone.
